title: Coast to Coast Radio Program! Commercial Free! Feb 1st thru Feb
description:
Here we are again, another eight broadcasts of the greatest late night radio program ever, Coast to Coast! I hope you all enjoy and spread the knowledge. Seed and inform others. Thanks in advance to all the seeders. Until next week my friends. Stokeman Out......

Friday February 1st, 2008
Night of Open Lines

Host: Ian Punnett
Guest(s): Open Lines

Saturday February 2nd, 2008
Programmed Reality
Electrical engineer and scientific truth seeker Jim Elvidge discussed evidence that shows we could be living in a programmed reality, in which "everything [we] perceive is under program control or is generated by some computational mechanism."
Host: Ian Punnett
Guest(s): Jim Elvidge, Gregg McBride

Sunday February 3rd, 2008
Ancient Astronaut Theory

Host: George Noory
Guest(s): Giorgio Tsoukalos, Mary Ann Winkowksi

Monday February 4th, 2008
Psi Research

Host: George Noory

Tuesday February 5th, 2008
Weather Modification

Host: George Noory

Wednesday February 6th, 2008
New Technolgy & Geopolitics

Dowsing & Remote Viewing for Gain

Friday February 8th, 2008
Moments of Evil & More
